WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.880
You know I can take care of myself.

00:03.680 --> 00:04.340
Yeah, I know.

00:05.020 --> 00:05.840
It's not for you.

00:06.920 --> 00:07.580
It's for me.

00:08.860 --> 00:09.560
For us.

00:11.260 --> 00:14.140
You make me brave enough to admit that I want to be happy.

00:15.940 --> 00:17.460
And I want to be happy with you.

00:23.340 --> 00:25.080
And I'm gonna pick up more catering shifts.

00:26.660 --> 00:27.780
And ask for a raise.

00:28.820 --> 00:31.500
I'll find a serving job at an actual restaurant.

00:32.940 --> 00:35.860
And I won't say no to commercial auditions even though they're annoying.

00:36.740 --> 00:38.600
I'll make an actual effort to find a manager.
